Title: BoF: Craft Supply Swap
Book Description: Birds of a Feather: Are your jewelry making supplies gathering dust and you find yourself really into embroidery instead? Why not offload your unused crafting items and pick up some things you can use?

Title: Consent Expectations and Party Vetting Opportunity
Book Description: This is a primer on dungeon policies and expectations specific to the Jett's Arcade Dungeon Party. If you want to attend the Dungeon Party- be sure to attend one of the consent panels and be vetted. This event is 18+.

Title: Fetish and Fluff: The Curious Side of the Furry Fandom
Book Description: This panel is to dive into the curiosity that is the fetish side of the furry fandom. This event is 18+.
